QuestData.Title: Die Fishman Die
QuestData.Description: A fish ate my wolf, and murlocs look like fish. I'm going to make those murlocs pay!$b$bHead back down to the canyon and kill the fishmen! My wolf will be avenged!
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 4 Coldlight Hunters and 4 Coldlight Oracles.
QuestData.RewardText: I know, murlocs aren't fish. I thought that killing them would make me feel better, but I still feel sad about my wolf.$b$b<Orako sighs.>
